data.value: *There are only a few steps left before you can complete the sale process. 1-) First of all, you need to click the "Calculate" button after determining the total alterations. (If you change the service type, you have to click again.) 2-) After the complete calculation step, you can click the "Finish" button, which is placed right at the bottom of the page, and see the general report.
